# migrated from tests/cases/agent_search.it.chat (gen346, hermetic + isolated)
[mock hermetic]
!set PARROT0_BASE=
!set PARROT0_SESSION=
!set PARROT0_WORLD_FACTS=0
!set PARROT0_LANG=en
!reset

[test agent_search.it]
# gen119 (rung 19 + rung 13) — bilingual ratchet for the planner agent. The same
# breadth-first search over the action space runs from an Italian instruction:
# the planning competence lives in the algorithm. Only the framing words differ
# (da, usando, raggiungere); the actions, the search, and the plan report — with
# its real replayed trajectory — are shared.

# Synthesize the shortest plan from 4 to 13 with {x3, +1}: x3, +1.
> da 4, usando times 3 and add 1, raggiungere 13.
< Reached 13 from 4 in 2 steps: 4 -[*3]-> 12 -[+1]-> 13.

# A held-out goal: from 2 to 24 with {+2, x2} — the shortest plan is 4 steps.
> da 2, usando add 2 and times 2, raggiungere 24.
< Reached 24 from 2 in 4 steps: 2 -[+2]-> 4 -[+2]-> 6 -[*2]-> 12 -[*2]-> 24.

